data.description: Step into this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom renovated home nestled in an up and coming area of College Park. With the city's future plans to rejuvenate over 700 acres, including the Old National Corridor, this home presents not just a beautiful residence but a smart investment. Inside, enjoy the convenience of a primary bedroom on the main floor, along with new HVAC, updated lighting, and a charming gas fireplace. The renovated features continue with updated bathrooms including new vanities and tile flooring throughout. Upstairs, discover ample space including a sitting area and bonus room. Security is ensured with a Ring camera, alarm system, and HVAC cage. Outside, find tranquility on the beautiful deck, around the firepit, or amidst an array of fruit trees and herbs including apple, peach, and fig trees. Plus, a handy shed provides storage for yard or garden tools. Located conveniently to College Park, East Point, and the Atlanta Airport, this home offers both comfort and accessibility, inviting you to make it yours today.
